UAE Board::Social Media Account Manager - Abu Dhabi
Social Media Account Manager - Abu Dhabi Media
Account Manager will lead a team of Account Executives managing one of the largest social media accounts in the UAE. Team is fully responsible for everything to do with content creation, community management, coming up with creative concepts, liaising with creative team, managing campaigns & activations, etc.
Account Manager will be in daily communication with management at client side for approvals & regular requests. The candidate must have prior experience managing large social media initiatives.
This is an exciting & truly challenging opportunity - requires dedication & experience.
